{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "1eab93a5-fe7a-4feb-b13a-687bf0dda215", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/1eab93a5-fe7a-4feb-b13a-687bf0dda215@1.pkg/1772597556574/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597557433", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/1eab93a5-fe7a-4feb-b13a-687bf0dda215@1.pkg/1772597556574/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597557433"}, "identifier": "1eab93a5-fe7a-4feb-b13a-687bf0dda215", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p><strong>选项A错误，当今国际关系主流仍是和平与发展，竞争与合作并存，非单纯冲突。&nbsp; </strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>选项B正确，中国通过WTO机制协商的回应，体现了经济全球化下应通过多边规则解决争端，反对单边保护主义，符合教材中“经济全球化要求各国协商合作”的观点。&nbsp; </strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>选项C“主导”表述错误，中国是参与者而非主导者；</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>选项D与事实相悖，贸易保护主义加剧矛盾，违背全球化趋势。</strong></p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（改编）2025年3月，美国政府以“国家安全”为由，宣布对中国新能源汽车加征50%关税，并限制中国AI技术在美投资。中国商务部回应将采取必要措施维护权益，同时呼吁通过WTO机制协商解决。此举表明（ ）&nbsp;</p>\n", "title": "（改编）2025年3月，美国政府以“国家安全”为由，宣布对中国新能源汽车加征50%关税，并限制中国AI技术在美投资。中国商务部回应将采取必要措施维护权益，同时呼吁通过WTO机制协商解决。此举表明（ ） ", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/1eab93a5-fe7a-4feb-b13a-687bf0dda215@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754998392698", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>竞争与冲突已成为当今国际关系的主流</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>经济全球化背景下各国应坚持公平竞争与多边协商&nbsp;</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>中国主导全球治理体系改革，推动国际新秩序建立</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>贸易保护主义是解决国际争端的最有效途径</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>（改编）2025年3月，美国政府以“国家安全”为由，宣布对中国新能源汽车加征50%关税，并限制中国AI技术在美投资。中国商务部回应将采取必要措施维护权益，同时呼吁通过WTO机制协商解决。此举表明（ ）&nbsp;</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "1eab93a5-fe7a-4feb-b13a-687bf0dda215", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "（改编）2025年3月，美国政府以“国家安全”为由，宣布对中国新能源汽车加征50%关税，并限制中国AI技术在美投资。中国商务部回应将采取必要措施维护权益，同时呼吁通过WTO机制协商解决。此举表明（ ） "}, "global_description": {"zh-CN": "<p>（改编）2025年3月，美国政府以“国家安全